| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3174 — Recovery Inhibition (worldleaks)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: edff77e6-0cfb-591a-8b6e-f14a6b8ea92f"
